name: MTLDynamicLibraryError.Code
desc: Error codes that Metal can generate when creating dynamic libraries.

items.name: case compilationFailure
items.desc: Metal could not compile the dynamic library.

items.name: case dependencyLoadFailure
items.desc: The dynamic library couldn’t link to the specified dynamic libraries.

items.name: case invalidFile
items.desc: The file for the dynamic library isn’t valid.

items.name: case unresolvedInstallName
items.desc: Metal could not resolve the installation name for the new dynamic library.

items.name: case unsupported
items.desc: The Metal device object does not support dynamic libraries.
